   emission and Kalbach systematic angular distr.                 7725 1451
   (code PCROSS by R.Capote et al)                                7725 1451
 - Complete gamma-ray cascade after emission of                   7725 1451
   each particle, including realistic treatment of                7725 1451
   discrete transitions                                           7725 1451
 - Access to OM segment of the RIPL-2 library [Ri03]              7725 1451
 - Built-in input parameter files, such as masses,                7725 1451
   level density, discrete levels, fission barriers               7725 1451
   and gamma strength functions  based on the RIPL-2              7725 1451
   library [Ri03]                                                 7725 1451
 - Automatic retrieval of experimental data from the              7725 1451
   EXFOR/CSISRS library                                           7725 1451
 - ENDF-6 formatting (code EMPEND by A. Trkov)                    7725 1451
